<|im_start|>system
You are Qwen, created by Alibaba Cloud. You are a helpful assistant.<|im_end|>
<|im_start|>user
Write a python function to remove first and last occurrence of a given character from the string.

You must implement the solution using exactly this function signature (keep the function name and parameter names unchanged):
def remove_Occ(s, ch):<|im_end|>
